  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Afghans Work on Climate Change</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education and action is needed to create sustained change. Everyone at our Learning Centers, health clinics, workshops, events, private schools, and listeners to Radio Meraj, get messages about the environment. We run projects that directly address climate change such as tree and shrub planting, clean up campaigns and resource management at centers.  Individual action is encouraged e.g.  buying and planting a tree. Mindsets need to change and everyone needs to take action.</narrative>
  </description>
